        <title type="html"><![CDATA[从文章到博客，不怕看到过的文章走丢]]></title>
        <id>https://yujiale.blog/post/cong-wen-zhang-dao-bo-ke-bu-pa-kan-dao-guo-de-wen-zhang-zou-diu/</id>
        <link href="https://yujiale.blog/post/cong-wen-zhang-dao-bo-ke-bu-pa-kan-dao-guo-de-wen-zhang-zou-diu/">
        </link>
        <updated>2022-04-26T08:14:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>将网站内容快速保存到Notion，并快速发布到个人博客。文章404从此不再有，分享文章处处可及。</p>
]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>将网站内容快速保存到Notion，并快速发布到个人博客。文章404从此不再有，分享文章处处可及。</p>
<!-- more -->
<blockquote>
<p>本文由 <a href="http://ksria.com/simpread/">简悦 SimpRead</a> 转码， 原文地址 <a href="https://article.yujiale.blog/article/from-website-to-blog">article.yujiale.blog</a></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>快来找我玩呀~</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id=""><a href="#30e13c1bb0c747d181742302f845afed" title="写在前面"></a>写在前面</h3>
<p>本配置预计用时 40 分钟左右，熟练者或已经进行过相关配置者用时 20 分钟左右。此教程不需要编程技巧。</p>
<h3 id="-2"><a href="#e29f39f7906b4b07b80ec3f0e84c204d" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h3>
<p>本教程需要用到的内容有：</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><a href="http://ksria.com/simpread/">简悦</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://vercel.com/">Vercel</a> 账号</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a> 账号</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://www.notion.so/">Notion</a> 账号</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>良好的网络环境</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>中学以上英语水平</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>中等水平的理解能力🧠</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>一颗愿意折腾的心❤️</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="-3"><a href="#6fe731cc203b4a00b4b521f4cf9c3a25" title="整体思路"></a>整体思路</h3>
<p>将简悦提供的模板和博客网站需要的模板融合起来，让新模板具有两者都能够识别的属性。通过简悦插件将文章保存到 Notion 后，自动填写这些属性，并让博客服务识别并转换生成博客文章。</p>
<h4 id="-4"><a href="#fd662ee2920243c58b5f0dff8f71d08d" title="需要用到的Token"></a>需要用到的 Token</h4>
<ul>
<li>
<p>简悦 Integration Token <a href="https://www.notion.so/my-integrations">创建⤴️</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Notion Page ID <a href="https://article.yujiale.blog/article/5fd315d7d2fc4f8389a8064bd037b146">找到它</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="-5"><a href="#08c1323ba81e43a0885d69175fda7a81" title="需要用到的页面"></a>需要用到的页面</h4>
<ul>
<li>
<p>简悦模板 👉 <a href="https://article.yujiale.blog/article/e784eba882da452eb8f300e6cd6b195d">复制</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="http://noto.so/">noto.so</a> 官网 👉<a href="https://noto.so/">直达</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Nobelium GitHub 仓库 👉<a href="https://github.com/craigary/nobelium">直达</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>NotionNext GitHub 仓库 👉<a href="https://github.com/tangly1024/NotionNext">直达</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>简悦 Notion 增强辅助插件 👉<a href="https://simpread.ksria.cn/plugins/details/g60jwZEeqU">安装</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>简悦 Notion Blog 增强辅助插件 👉<a href="https://simpread.ksria.cn/plugins/details/iJdQjjoYAB">安装</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>官方剪藏插件 Notion Web Clipper 👉<a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/notion-web-clipper/knheggckgoiihginacbkhaalnibhilkk">安装</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="-6"><a href="#d973d542e8944f9d8c00115bcb42d8ee" title="开始折腾"></a>开始折腾</h3>
<p>我们以搭建 NotionNext 博客作为演示，使用 Nobelium、noto.so 的用户操作过程与 NotionNext 相似，我会在操作不一致的部分做说明，一步步照做即可。</p>
<ol>
<li>
<p>打开 Notion 网页版，复制 <a href="https://article.yujiale.blog/article/02ab3b8678004aa69e9e415905ef32a5">NotionNext 的模板</a>（Nobelium 的用户请复制 <a href="https://article.yujiale.blog/article/adc3552cfc73442ab5048d4b1eb0079a">Nobelium 模板</a>，noto.so 用户请复制 <a href="https://article.yujiale.blog/article/6a7a53697d814f0794992da8a9de9471">noto.so 模板</a>）；</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>安装 Notion 官方剪藏工具 <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/notion-web-clipper/knheggckgoiihginacbkhaalnibhilkk">Notion Web Clipper</a>，使用 Notion Web Clipper 保存任意一篇文章，保存时选择创建网页链接数据库，输入任意名称，如下图所示；</p>
</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F17efba60-11dd-4da8-82e5-9fa2a31591ae%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3D3d157e8cb43bfd748e7dabc4099777e7b86f2b0dca9c69ab65697d8b3b075129%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=99b3dc0b-655b-40e7-a292-bf0fcbff7bb5&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="3">
<li>返回到 Notion，找到刚刚创建的数据库，添加一个表格视图（table view），然后，为他添加一个名称是 <code>Origin</code> 的列表，属性是 <code>Select</code> ，如下图所示。然后，在 <code>Created</code> 一列上点击右键，删除这一列；</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F18a829d9-73cf-4f97-8413-c89620ed07c5%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3D93e30f7cfc9ba426de1d39bd974821d1323f1268e82ef4d37cfb148c76acded0%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=f7665727-5f39-4d2a-81d6-c131d3eb0dbc&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F2051e724-2dcf-49f7-882f-3eb0fb2db531%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3D6358360c99693218681d005e68c592c907302b07f40dd126a23914c3a2e2f472%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=632a8df2-15b9-4493-a060-f823311baede&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol>
<li>现在你的 Notion 工作区中应该有两个模板，一个是博客的模板，一个是简悦的模板，现在我们让简悦访问并识别这个页面，要做到这一点，我们<a href="https://www.notion.so/my-integrations">新建一个 Notion Integration</a>，选择新建（Create new integration）；</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2Ff1a97825-4892-476c-b4d7-c02822ddf6e6%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3Dedf147601990029e7f8e8d2639505c03583c4a75714c862b73911170bcf731ab%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=e5c4bb04-7b32-4fab-8570-13105d11a198&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="2">
<li>紧接着，请按照图示进行相关设置，名称和头像自拟。最后选择提交（Submit）</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2Fa9049dd1-b851-4caa-8459-2b5f07e97dd6%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3D3f1d5c1a595f824301904c2a586fafdbc8ef75f97316f39db53176ed61d1509f%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=7be5c600-533c-48b0-bfcf-92ed8c2012bd&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="3">
<li>点击展示（Show）并复制（Copy）页面中给出的 Internal Integration Token，保存好这串内容；</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F4be50aea-f37a-4f67-a55e-781ee91181c2%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3D4b488bcea8ecebf65940ee39715d8ae4adb2b2c7303a88aac8d987a1b0f77ad8%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=8a94516c-28b9-49a2-ab18-392321e2626b&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol>
<li>回到之前我们修改过的简悦 Notion 模板中，在右上角找到 Share，邀请我们刚刚创建的简悦 Integration；</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="7"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F272a1e34-1f74-4d52-acea-5f4774abf805%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3D9f02bad8e94600567a13352e6b77197061c030513deb985dc3088d31ffcbd6df%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=79480f34-cb36-48f5-bed6-6782f01830df&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="2">
<li>将页面分享到互联网上（Share to web），并复制这个页面的链接；</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="8"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F79237421-91a0-459c-8a94-e2a342369890%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3D9c5679384aa6ce43c7deeb4f0ddb110083abba50499dcd3536b8901bde01acce%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=4d294ae1-9664-4a84-9ca2-9978a124c2af&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="3">
<li>将链接复制到浏览器地址栏，他应该是类似 <code>[https://www.notion.so/abcd****xyz?v=123***789](https://www.notion.so/abcd****xyz?v=123***789)</code></li>
</ol>
<p>的一个结构，我们复制 <code>[https://www.notion.so/](https://www.notion.so/abcd****xyz?v=123***789)</code> 后面 <code>[abcd****xyz](https://www.notion.so/abcd****xyz?v=123***789)</code> 这一部分内容，得到这个页面的 ID，同样，保存好这部分内容；</p>
<ol>
<li>
<p>在简悦选项页授权 Notion 并选择将文章保存到刚刚我们设置好的页面，安装简悦插件<a href="https://simpread.ksria.cn/plugins/details/g60jwZEeqU">导入到 Notion 辅助增强</a>和 <a href="https://simpread.ksria.cn/plugins/details/iJdQjjoYAB">Notion blog 辅助增强</a>。注意：如果使用同步助手请先关闭同步助手，然后安装插件；</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>打开任意一篇文章，配置 Notion 辅助增强，点击导入到 Notion 辅助增强选项进行设置。如果插件未生效请重新卸载安装，并检查是否关闭同步助手；</p>
</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="9"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F792701f5-e344-4c8e-ba7b-edf3fb466821%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3D079d39090d989b3356e135520d2c8b4b65c6e50ed7cd52c3ded8037abed5d4c3%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=077abaac-0c1d-4be4-83ca-30fa17270366&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="3">
<li>将我们保存的简悦 Internal Integration Token 填入第一栏，将简悦 Internal Integration Token 和页面 ID 填入第二栏，点击保存并关闭；</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="10"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2Fe4b3423f-b758-4344-9c78-e0e2be2a1559%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3D897bf61907c80634725bdd9e6daf006204938a7e83097b081adaa4ef9182f27a%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=b0a25c6e-ec5e-4d82-8018-2c2ddc2fcc3c&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol>
<li>同样的，我们设置 <a href="https://simpread.ksria.cn/plugins/details/iJdQjjoYAB">Notion blog 辅助增强</a>，将我们保存的简悦 Internal Integration Token 填入第一栏，将简悦 Internal Integration Token 和页面 ID 填入第二栏，选择保存并关闭；</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="11"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F815db51c-5a00-4e63-a30c-266052e08b7c%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3Db4aac442f7d3f8817f3c1df363c9ca922fc3a682c9340146c101190597ef72d5%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=7ed89698-10a4-4b07-8a5a-5034cf88352a&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="2">
<li>
<p>随后，我们将这篇文章保存到 Notion，看看是否成功，如果不成功，请检查上述步骤是否设置有误，如果无法排查，请移步简悦官方反馈渠道反馈；</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>确保简悦可以识别并保存文章到 Notion 后，我们下一步将 NotionNext 模板和简悦模板合并。（Nobelium 用户与 NotionNext 一致，但下方会略有不同）要做到这一点，我们首先点击 NotionNext 的模板页面，选中所有页面，将所有内容移动到简悦模板页面中。这时，你会发现简悦模板中比原先多出了一些列，这是因为 Notion 在复制页面的过程中，将原先 NotionNext 的一些列也复制到了简悦模板中来。这节省了我们手动复制的时间，也不容易出错。</p>
</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="12"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2Ff65ec683-8c73-4910-a23c-7a6d6e7f0c8d%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3D476b458afafb1d7e092cc8cd69dd1b4f8ad885ce7d0fe54e0dc9309fde5959a5%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=59a95b25-09bc-4051-aa91-9086e861a1d4&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="2">
<li>随后，我们将页面 Name 一列改为 title，再添加一列 tags，将属性选择为 <code>Multi-select</code>。并最后检查有无页面的列被漏掉了。原则是简悦和博客模板的所有列都应该被加入这个模板中，两者冲突的部分（例如标题）遵照博客的模板设置，）；</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="13"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F821a0de3-7a00-4324-978e-29a2b7579b26%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3Df99e94c82ab440c043da89606d7089a8c061d6d7ec4cef85c379e51c8e3eec6c%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=9d4679d6-722f-4606-914c-56f5b3eacecf&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="14"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F4a94c1b7-98e6-4a68-aa94-39efbe13d1d7%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3Dcfde4de8ddbe0010d1393e3f76ecc97e50d10066981bd982a8fd6eea67f1ecc6%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=ee0a6ceb-4347-43b9-a9bc-27ed48c15402&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="3">
<li>（仅限 NotionNext）这样，我们 Notion 模板和简悦的部分就设置完成了，下面进入 NotionNext 的搭建。进入我们 Fork <a href="https://github.com/tangly1024/NotionNext/fork">NotionNext 仓库</a>。如果你已经搭建好了博客，请忽略此步；</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="15"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F46ca6188-4c7f-4b6a-a9f7-b91a671e2fb6%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3Dd278909fc4329149e4f47864d2d589892526c5a0f1f292a945c4892e3407d994%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=c454ad9b-4869-4f41-bf37-e9b3286fb31b&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="5">
<li>
<p>（仅限 NotionNext）进入到我们复制好的仓库，点击<code>blog.config.js</code> 修改它，在如图所示的地方添加页面 ID（Page ID），然后按照[</p>
<p>NotionNext</p>
<p>tangly1024 • Updated on 2022-04-26</p>
<p>](https://github.com/tangly1024/NotionNext)的官方说明对其他地方做修改；</p>
</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="16"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F3b0367f8-f643-46fa-81c8-79f19bb5a341%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3Da2566157cc43ff990317dacaae195416532840e0441930ef74461eaf182cd079%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=8b0961f7-db27-4db7-b1db-701659e734e2&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="7">
<li>（仅限 Nobelium） Nebelium 用户请 Fork <a href="https://github.com/craigary/nobelium/fork">Nobelium 仓库</a>，如果你已经搭建好了博客，请忽略此步；</li>
<li>（仅限 Nobelium）进入到我们复制好的仓库，点击 <code>blog.config.js</code> 修改它，按照注释修改相关的内容；</li>
<li>进入 Vercel，选择新建项目（+New Project），选择我们刚刚创建或修改的 GitHub 仓库，等待部署（Deploy）完成。Nobelium 用户需要在部署时添加环境变量，在左侧输入<code>NOTION_PAGE_ID</code> ，在右侧输入你的页面 ID（Page ID），点击添加（Add）后部署（Deploy）。部署完成后稍等几分钟你应该可以访问到博客并且有示例文章显示出来。</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="17"><img src="https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F0ee9ad09-618a-40eb-8ec5-f6d71cba0722%2FUntitled.png%3FX-Amz-Algorithm%3DAWS4-HMAC-SHA256%26X-Amz-Content-Sha256%3DUNSIGNED-PAYLOAD%26X-Amz-Credential%3DAKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%252F20220426%252Fus-west-2%252Fs3%252Faws4_request%26X-Amz-Date%3D20220426T081641Z%26X-Amz-Expires%3D86400%26X-Amz-Signature%3Def4b433dc8057d9105b17b0d93278a3de50d8a48ab914fd9b75798186475feff%26X-Amz-SignedHeaders%3Dhost%26x-id%3DGetObject?table=block&amp;id=540993b9-f483-4f1e-bd6e-5188e458ed90&amp;cache=v2" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol start="11">
<li>最后，我们选择一篇文章，进入简悦的阅读模式，选择，保存到 Notion 然后点击 Notion blog 辅助增强，选择发布此文章，点击生成，过一会文章就会出现在博客文章里了。</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="-7"><a href="#64c7b2be6c134e48a2edf3820832dd69" title="避坑指南"></a>避坑指南</h3>
<ol start="13">
<li>要邀请创建的简悦集成（Integration）到数据库（Database）简悦 Notion 增强辅助插件才可以将内容保存到 Notion；</li>
<li>简悦 Notion Blog 增强导出失败可以先检查 Notion 数据库中是否有这篇文章；</li>
<li>博客搭建成功但没有文章显示可以查看 Notion 数据库（Database）的模板是否与相应的模板一致，文章标题列的名称应为 title；</li>
<li>博客搭建成功后点击文章报错 client side error 可能需要检查 Notion 数据库中是否有 Created 这一列，如有，可以删掉。</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
